originalText.text:
Paul was supposed to deliver our wedding photos over two months ago as he promised via email and as written in our contract.

However, he has ignored all communication the last 2 months no matter how many times we have tried to reach out to him. We have no idea what has happened to our wedding photos and don't know if we will ever receive them.

We unfortunately have suffered a very frustrating experience working with Paul and would not recommend him.

originalText.text: Where do I start! I have known Paul from when I got engaged and worked with him for my engagement pictures and wedding pictures. When I said he BLEW it out of the water, Paul Woo did AMAZING. To this day I still swoon over my wedding pictures. Fast forward 5 years later, and I find out he is in town doing mini-shoots. I of course jump at the opportunity cause now, my family is no longer just me and my husband, but 2 kiddos too. Just received the pictures and OMG, wow! Anyone who has done pictures with kids knows how exhausting it can be, but Paul was so amazing, calm and captured the perfect shots of my kids and my family. I CANNOT wait to be a regular doing family shoots with him. If you're looking for beyond amazing pictures, please look no further, cause let me tell you, you will be BLOWN away by the talent of this man. Simply amazing! :)

originalText.text:
Paul provided me amazing pictures of my proposal. He not only captured a moment in time, he provided helpful guidance and insight into a journey that I didn't even know I needed.  Luckily for me, Paul has witnessed countless proposals and was able to help me calm my nerves, prepare my lines, and thankfully not bumble my way through a big life milestone. All the while, he was discreet, accommodating, and allowed for my big moment to unfold without any additional stressors.  He was professional, easygoing, with an eye for capturing the essence of the moment.

Would highly recommend!

originalText.text: Working with Paul throughout our engagement and wedding was everything we had hoped for - even in adapting and pivoting through the changes and plans we made because of Covid-19's impact on our wedding, Paul was professional and flexible in working with us during such a stressful time. He really brought a calm and understanding to the experience that I think we needed. For both our engagement shoot and wedding day, we put all our trust in Paul for direction and were so incredibly happy with the results. The photos are beautiful and Paul has a truly unique, artistic eye.

originalText.text: Paul Woo is a fantastic photographer and a wonderful professional to work with.  He put everyone at ease,  communicated well, and delivered our photos in a timely manner- not to mention they are exactly what we hoped for.  He captures colors and forms beautifully.  His work is artful and he works very hard. I would recommend him highly- we are beyond thrilled with our wedding photos!!
